Error demo

Attached video capture of Bug Description..

This means that JRE you are executing the RAC with (1.4.2) is different than the JRE used to generate the JUnit code with.  

In Eclipse, go to Window->Preferences->Java->Compiler and set the Compiler Compliance to 1.4.  You must then regenerate the JUnit test and then execute again. 

This worked for me.  If this does not solve the problem, please resubmit or reopen the defect.
Verified and the problem doesnot exists.
